" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個大屁股，淫奶又大又白 格肋底又滑又香 質個頭入去索 舔到佢啲淫肉全部都係口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用佢對淫奶同大臀肉打我臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用碌鳩打磨拍佢塊淫臉+奶 令佢成身都充滿住碌鳩嘅雄性味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用兩塊大臀肉同大淫奶玩臀交同夾腸同腋交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n狗仔式打屁股一邊打一邊問喺咪淫婦喺咪成日故意露奶誘惑人屌佢 再屌到佢叫老公 邊問邊大大力打佢個大屁股 再屌到佢個大屁股搖黎搖去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女下男上張腿當打椿機咁屌 最好屌一下啲淫水擠一大堆出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從佢背後用手托開對淫腳令佢正面咁屌 等佢自己睇睇下啲淫水幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中出之餘一定要射到佢成身都係精 再用有殘餘精液嘅大龜頭拍佢臉+磨嘴唇<br />\n最後塞入口等佢舔乾淨 令佢變成性奴液便器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f0974aeae5a00bf5d734291e61d94e556e6d2f3","tid":778790,"uid":27719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T03:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}